cu.explanation_en: Setting ipv4 to "192.168.70.132.1" (invalid IP format) will cause the CU to fail binding to the AMF address, leading to unreachable AMF connection.

du.explanation_en: Setting local_n_address to "127.0.0.3.4" (invalid IP format) will cause the DU to fail binding to the address, leading to unreachable F1 interface.
